{"tid":1081971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 議員2024年開始無腦用","createTime":"2019-03-28T15:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T16:10:57.000Z","uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48ceddc34f5dd0d98a52cd764a628319c851feb0","tid":1081971,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPdrm3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPdrm3z.jpg&h=609f507c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信八方一話議員冇「腦」，有啲人就會諗係邊個呢？不過八方講緊嘅係全體議員。<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，現時立法會秘書處係會畀每一位議員一部電腦，作為接駁立法會內聯網之用。不過隨住科技進步，秘書處準備由下屆立法會開始將內聯網嘅服務都搬埋上互聯網，等議員喺自己部機都用到秘書處嘅服務，所以唔打算再配給電腦畀議員喇。<br />\n<br />\n作為過渡安排，連任到下屆立法會嘅議員可以繼續用秘書處提供嘅電腦，直至2024年9月，或者趁下個月秘書處幫議員更新部電腦嗰陣，還返部機畀秘書處。<br />\n<br />\n秘書處能夠將啲服務由內聯網搬上互聯網當然係好事啦，不過切記要做好啲保安，唔係被人入侵就麻煩喇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190328&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59423930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190328%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59423930&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=472683bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190328%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59423930&h=8cd157f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190328&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59423930</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你蘋果個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe88729a7ba37db601e1bd2f1b3743b7169f6fc","tid":1081971,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"係咪仲用緊IE?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b52b971f731f54160b8c6a1dd11b0d1f9a677ad","tid":1081971,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe88729a7ba37db601e1bd2f1b3743b7169f6fc","tid":1081971,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"係咪仲用緊IE?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"政府department啲內聯網好多IE先開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}